A developer implements a theming system with CSS custom properties and cascade layers:

```css
@layer tokens, base, components;

@layer tokens {
  :root {
    --radius: 4px;
    --spacing-md: 16px;
  }
  :root[data-theme="rounded"] {
    --radius: 12px;
  }
}

@layer base {
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
}

@layer components {
  .card {
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
  }
}

/* Theme override added later by a plugin */
.card { border-radius: 0; }
```

